hadiths[16]{hadithnumber,text}:
2859,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney sirate-mustaqim ki misal di hai, us sirate-mustaqim key dono janib do ghar hain, un gharon key darwazey khuley huye hain, darwazon par pardey padey huye hain, eik pukarney wala us raastey key sirey par khada pukar raha hai, aur doosra pukarney wala ooper sey pukar raha hai, (phir aap ney ye aayat padhi) (والله يدعوا إلى دار السلام ويهدي من يشاء إلى صراط مستقيم) '' Allah Taala darus-slam ( jannat ki taraf ( bulata hai aur jisey chahta hai'' sirate-mustaqim '' ki hidayat deta hai'' , to wo darwazey jo sirate-mustaqim key dono janib hain wo hudoodullah hain padhi. to koi shakhs jab tak parda khol na diya jaey, hudoodullah main dakhil nahin ho sakta aur ooper sey pukarney wala uskey rab ka waaiz hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- mainey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman ko suna wo kehtey they ke mainey Zakariya bin Adi ko suna wo kehtey they ke Abu-Is-haq Fazari ney kaha : baqiya ( Raavi ( tum sey jo Suqa raawiyon key zariey riwayat karen usey ley lo aur Ismail bin Ayash ki riwayat na lo chahey wo Suqa sey riwayat karen ya ghair Suqa sey ."
2860,"eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hum logon key paas aaye aur farmaya : ''mainey khuwab dekha hai ke Jibreel merey sar key paas hain aur mekaael merey pairon key paas, un dono mein sey eik apney doosrey sathi sey keh raha tha : unki koi misal pesh karo, to usney aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko mukhatib kartey huye kaha : aap sunen, aap key kaan hamesha suntey rahen, aap samjhen, aap ka dil aql (samajh, ilm o hikmat) sey bhara rahey. aap ki misal aur aap ki ummat ki misal eik aisey badshah ki hai jisney eik shehar abad kya, us shehar main eik ghar banaya phir eik dastarkhuwan bichaya, phir qaasid ko bhej kar logon ko khaney par bulaya, to kuch logon ney uski dawat qubul kar li aur kuch logon ney bulaney waley ki dawat thukra di (kuch parwah hi na ki) is misal mein ye samjho ke Allah badshah hai, aur ''daar'' sey murad Islam hai aur '' bait '' sey murad jannat hai aur aap aey Muhammad! Rasool o qaasid hain. jisney aap ki dawat qubul kar li wo Islam mein dakhil ho gaya aur jo Islam mein dakhil ho gaya wo jannat mein dakhil ho gaya to usney wo sab kuch khaya jo jannat mein hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai aur wo sandaein is hadees ki sanad sey ziyada sahih hain, 2- ye mursal hadees hai (yani munqataa hai) 3- Saeed bin abi Hilal ney Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) ko nahin paya hai, 4- is bab mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai) jo aagey aa rahi hai) ."
2861,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Isha padhi. phir paltey to Abdullah bin Masood ka haath apney haath mein ley liya aur unhen sath liye huye Makka ki pathreeli zamin ki taraf nikal gaey ( wahan ( unhen (eik jagah ( bitha diya. phir unkey chaaron taraf lakeerein khinch den , aur un sey kaha : ''in lakeeron sey bahar nikal kar hergiz na jana. tumharey qarib bahut sey log aa kar rukengey lekin tum unsey baat na karna, aur wo khud bhi tum sey baat na kerengey.'' Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jahan jana chahtey they wahan chaley gaey, usi doran ke main apney daayre key andar betha huwa tha kuchh log merey paas aaye wo jaat lag rahey they, unkey baal aur jism na mujhey nangey dikhai dey rahey they aur na hi ( unkey jismon par mujhey ( libas nazar aa raha tha, wo merey paas aa kar ruk jatey aur lakeer ko paar na kartey , phir wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki taraf nikal jatey , yahan tak ke jab raat khatam honey ko aai to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas tashrif laye, main betha huwa tha. aap ney farmaya : ''raat hi sey apney aap ko dekhta hun (yani main so na saka) phir aap daaerey key andar dakhil ho kar merey paas aaye. aur meri raan ka takiya bana kar so gaey, aap soney mein kharraatey leney lagtey they, to usi doran ke main betha huwa tha aur aap meri raan ka takiya banaey huye so rahey they. yakayak mainey apney aap ko aisey logon key darmiyan paya jinkey kapdey safed they, Allah khub janta hai ke unhen kis qadr khoobsurti hasil thi. wo log merey paas aa kar ruk gaey, un mein sey kuchh log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sarhaaney beth gaey aur kuchh log aap key paaitaane, phir un logon ney aapas mein baaten kartey huye kaha : hamney kisi bandey ko kabhi nahin dekha jisey itna mila ho jitna is Nabi ko mila hai. in ki aankhen soti hain aur inka dil bedaar rehta hai. inkey liye koi misal pesh karo (phir unhoney kaha inki misal) eik sardar ki misal hai jisney eik mehal banaya , phir eik dastar khuwan bichhaya aur logon ko apney dastar khuwan par khaney peeney key liye bulaya , to jisney un ki dawat qubul kar li wo unkey khaney peeney sey faiz-yaab huwa. aur jisney un ki dawat qubul na ki wo (sardar) usey saza dega phir wo log uth kar chaley gaey. aur unkey jatey hi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bedaar ho gaey. aap ney farmaya : ''suna , kya kaha unhoney? aur ye kon log they? mainey kaha : Allah aur Allah key Rasool ziyada behtar jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : ''wo farishtey they. tum samajhtey ho unhoney kya misal di hai?'' mainey (phir) kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada behtar samajhtey hain. aap ney farmaya : ''unhoney jo misal di hai wo hai Rehman (Allah) Tabarak o taala ki, Rehman ney jannat banai , aur apney bandon ko jannat ki dawat di. to jisney dawat qubul kar li wo jannat mein dakhil ho gaya aur jo uski dawat na qubul kerega wo usey azab aur saza sey dochaar kerega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- abu Tameema : Hijaimi hain aur inka naam Tareef bin Mujaalid hai. 3- abu-Usman Nahdi ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Mul hai. 4- Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi jin sey ye hadees Moa'tamir ney riwayat ki hai wo Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Tarkhaan hain, wo asal mein Taimi na they, lekin wo banu Taim mein aaya jaya kartey they jiski wajeh sey wo Taimi mashhoor ho gaey. Ali ibne-Madeeni kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed kehtey they : mainey Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi sey ziyada kisi ko Allah sey darney wala nahin dekha."
2862,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri misal aur mujh sey pehley key anbiya ki misal, us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney ghar banaya, ghar ko mukammal kiya aur usey khoobsurat banaya, siwaye eik eent ki jagah key. log us ghar mein aaney lagey aur usey dekh kar tajjub karney lagey, aur kehney lagey : kaash! ye eik eent ki jagah (bhi) khaali na hoti.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2863,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney Yahya bin Zakariya (Aleh.)  ko paanch baaton ka hukm diya ke wo khud in par amal karen aur Bani-Israel ko bhi in par amal karney ka hukm den. qarib tha ke wo us hukm ki taameel mein susti aur takheer karen Esa (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : Allah Taala ney tumhen paanch baaton ka hukm diya hai ke tum khud un par amal karo aur Bani-Israel ko bhi hukm do ke wo bhi is par amal karen, ya to tum in ko hukm do ya phir main in ko hukm deta hun. Yahya ney kaha : main darta hun ke agar aap ney un umoor par mujh sey sabqat ki to main zamin mein dhansa na diya jaaun ya azab mein mubtala na kar diya jaaun, phir unhoney logon ko Baitul-Maqdis mein jama kiya, masjid logon sey bhar gaee. log kanguron par bhi ja bethey, phir unhoney kaha : Allah ney hamen paanch baaton ka hukm diya hai ke main khud bhi un par amal karun aur tumhen hukm dun ke tum bhi in par amal karo. pehli chiz ye hai ke tum Allah ki ibadat karo, aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek na karo, aur us shakhs ki misal jisney Allah key sath shirk kiya us aadmi ki hai jisney eik ghulam khalis apney maal sey sona ya chaandi dey kar kharid , aur (us sey) kaha : ye mera ghar hai aur ye mera paisha (roz-gaar) hai to tum kaam karo aur munaafa mujhey do, so wo kaam karta hai aur nafa apney Malik key siwa kisi aur ko deta hai, to bhala kon shakhs ye pasand kar sakta hai ke uska ghulam us qisam ka ho. aur Allah Taala ney tumhen namaz ka hukm diya hai to jab tum namaz padho to idhar udhar na dekho. kyonkey Allah apna chehra namaz padhtey huye bandey key chehrey ki taraf rakhta hai jab tak ke wo idhar udhar na dekhey. aur tumhen roza rakhney ka hukm diya hai. aur iski misal us aadmi ki hai jo eik jamaat key sath hai. uskey sath eik thaili hai jis mein mushk hai aur har eik ko uski khushbu bhaati hai. aur roze-daar key munh ki boo mushk ki khushbu sey badh kar hai. aur tumhen sadqa aur zakat deney ka hukm diya hai. iski misal us shakhs ki hai jisey dushman ney qaidi bana liya hai aur uskey haath uskey gardan sey mila kar baandh diye hain, aur usey ley kar chaley taake uski gardan uda den to us (qaidi) ney kaha ke merey paas thoda ziyada jo kuchh maal hai main tumhen fidya dey kar apney ko chuda lena chahta hun, phir unhen fidya dey kar apney ko azad kara liya. aur usney hukm diya hai ke tum Allah ka zikr karo. iski misal us aadmi ki misal hai jis ka peecha dushman tezi sey karey aur wo eik mazbut qile mein pahunch kar apni jaan ko un (dushmanon) sey bacha ley. aisey hi banda (insan) apney ko shetan (key shar) sey Allah key zikr key baghair nahin bacha sakta. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main bhi tumhen in paanch chizon ka hukm deta hun jinka hukm mujhey Allah ney diya hai (1) baat sunna. (2) (sunney key baad) itaat karna (3) jihad karna (4) hijrat karna (5) jamaat key sath rehna kyonkey jo jamaat sey eik baalisht bhi hata (alehda huwa) usney Islam ka patta apni gardan sey bahar nikal phenka. magar ye ke phir Islam mein wapis aa jaey. aur jisney jahiliyat ka na'ra lagaya to wo jahannam key indhanon mein sey eik endhan hai. (ye sun kar) eik shakhs ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! agar-che wo namaz padhey aur roza rakhey? aap ney farmaya : ''haan. agar-che wo namaz padhey aur roza rakhey. to tum Allah key bando ! us Allah ki pukar ki dawat do padhi. jisney tumhara naam Muslim aur momin rakha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Haris Ash-ari Sahabi hain aur is hadees key ilawa bhi un sey hadisein marvi (riwayat hui) hain."
2864,Haris Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah isi ki hum maana hadees riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- abu-Salaam Habshi ka naam Mamtur hai. 3- is hadees ko Ali bin Mubarak ney bhi Yahya bin Abi Kasir sey riwayat ki hai.
2865,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us momin ki misal jo Quran padhta hai santare ki si hai jiski khushbu bhi achchhi hai aur zaiqa aur maza bhi achchha hai, aur us momin ki misal jo Quran nahin padhta us khajoor ki si hai jis mein koi khushbu nahin hai aur maza mitha hai. aur us munafiq ki misal jo Quran padhta hai khushbudar paudey ki hai jiski boo,mehak to achchhi hai maza kadwa hai. aur us munafiq ki misal jo Quran nahin padhta hai (hanzal) (eik kadwa phal) ki tarah hai jiski boo bhi achchhi nahin aur maza bhi achchha nahin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Shoba ney Qatada sey bhi riwayat kiya hai."
2866,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin ki misal us kheti ki si hai jisey hawaeyn (idhar udhar) hilaati rehti hain. (aisa hi momin hai) momin par balaeyn barabar aati rehti hain, aur munafiq ki misal sanobar ( اشوک ( key darkht ki hai, wo apni jagah sey hiltaa nahin jab tak ke kaat na diya jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2867,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''darakhton main eik darkht aisa hai jiska patta nahin jhadta, ye momin ki misal hai to mujhey bataao ye kon sa darkht hai? Abdullah kehtey hain : log isey jangalon key darakhton mein dhoondney lagey , aur merey dil mein aaya ke ye khajoor ka darkht hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye khajoor hai''  mujhey sharam aa gaee ke main (chhota ho kar badon key samney) boloon ( jabke log khamosh hain) phir mainey (apney walid) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko wo baat batai jo merey dil mein aai thi, to unhoney kaha (merey betey) agar tum ney ye baat bata di hoti to ye chiz mujhey us sey ziyada aziz aur mehbub hoti ke merey paas us is tarah ka maal aur ye ye cheezen hotin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2868,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bhala bataao to sahih, agar tum mein sey kisi key darwazey par nehar ho aur wo us nehar mein har din paanch baar nahaaey to kya uskey jism par kuchh bhi mail kuchail rahega? Sahaba ney kaha : uskey jism par thoda bhi mail nahin rahega. aap ney farmaya : ''yehi misal hai paanchon namazon ki, un namazon ki barkat sey Allah Taala gunahon ko mita deta hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Quteba kehtey hain : hum sey Bakr bin Muzir Qarshi ney ibne Haad key wastey sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2869,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat ki misal barish ki hai, nahin kaha ja sakta ke uska awwal behtar hai ya uska aakhir.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ammar , Abdullah bin Amr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi sey riwayat hai ke wo Hammad bin Yahya Abeh ki taeed aur tasdeeq kartey they aur kehtey they ke wo hamarey asaatza (ustaadon) mein sey hain. faeeda padhi. : malum huwa ke ummat ka har fard bhalai key kamon main eik doosrey sey judaa huwa hai, nahin malum is mein sey kis ko kab aur kis waqt doosrey sey khair aur barkat pahunch jaey."
2870,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do kankariyaan phainktey huye farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ye kya hai aur ye kya hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko behtar malum hai. aap ney farmaya : ''ye ummid (aur aarzu) hai aur ye ajal (maut) hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
2871,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumhari muddat guzri hui ummaton key muqabil mein Asr sey maghrib tak ki darmiyani muddat ki tarah hai (yani bahut mukhtasar thodi) tumhari misal aur Yahud aur Nasara ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney kaee mazdoor rakhey. usney kaha : merey yahan kon eik qeeraat par dophare tak kaam karta hai? to Yahud ney eik eik qeeraat par kaam kiya, phir usney kaha : merey yahan kon mazduri karta hai dophare sey Asr tak eik eik qeeraat par? to Nasara ney eik qeeraat par kaam kiya. phir tum (musalman) kaam kartey ho Asr sey suraj doobney tak do do qeeraat par. (ye dekh kar) Yahud aur Nasara ghussa ho gaey, unhoney kaha : hamara kaam ziyada hai aur mazduri thodi hai?  Allah ney farmaya : kya tumhara haq kuch kam kar key mainey tum par zulm kiya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. to usney kaha : ye mera Fazal aur inaam hai main jisey chahun dun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2872,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log sau oont ki tarah hain. aadmi un mein sey eik bhi sawari key qabil nahin paata.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2873,"aur unhoney kaha : tum un main eik bhi sawari key qabil na paaogey, ya ye kaha : tum un mein sey sirf eik sawari key qabil paa sakogey."
2874,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri aur meri ummat ki misal us aadmi jaisi hai jisney aag jalaai to makkhiyaan aur patingey is mein padney lagey (yehi haal tumhara aur hamara hai) main tumhari kamar pakad pakad kar tumhen bacha raha hun aur tum ho ke is mein (jahannam ki aag mein) bila sochey samjhey ghusey chaley ja rahey ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
